Program: Last Word
Title: Lady Runcie, Wylie Vale, Israel Baker, Barry Reckord and Reginald Hill
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b019h3pp
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 Jan 2012
Matthew Bannister on The unconventional wife of the Archbishop of Canterbury, Lady Runcie The endocrinologist Wylie Vale who discovered the hormone that governs our response to stress, The violinist Israel Baker who played the searing music for the shower scene in Psycho The pioneering black playwright Barry Reckord And the crime novelist Reginald Hill, best known for creating Dalziel and Pascoe. Show less